OL,3,CCash-strapped Midlands councils call
OL,4,Cfor government help
OL,6,FCouncils across the Midlands have
OL,7,Fwarned Deputy Prime Minister Angela
OL,8,FRayner that the majority do not expect
OL,9,Fto meet their budget targets for the
OL,10,Fnext financial year, putting vital
OL,11,Fservices at risk.
OL,13,FThese councils are part of the Special
OL,14,FInterest Group of Municipal
OL,15,FAuthorities (Sigoma), which includes
OL,16,F48 councils outside of London.
OL,18,FThese councils serve 14 million people
OL,19,Facross southern ports, the Midlands,
OL,20,Fand the North.
