OL,3,CCash-strapped Midlands councils call
OL,4,Cfor government help
OL,6,FThe Midlands councils involved include:
OL,8,FIn a letter to Rayner ahead of the
OL,9,FLabour Party conference, Sir Stephen
OL,10,FHoughton, Labour chairman of Sigoma,
OL,11,Fcalled for urgent government action to
OL,12,Fstabilise local finances.
OL,14,FA survey of finance directors revealed
OL,15,Fthat only 3% of councils are confident
OL,16,Fthey can balance their books by 2025-
OL,17,F26, a sharp decline from 25% who felt
OL,18,Fconfident about their budgets for 2024-
OL,19,F25.
