OL,3,CCash-strapped Midlands councils call
OL,4,Cfor government help
OL,6,FServices such as children and adult
OL,7,Fsocial care are at particular risk.
OL,9,FOver 70% of councils believe
OL,10,Fchildren's social care services will
OL,11,Ffall below-required standards, and 65%
OL,12,Fexpressed concerns about maintaining
OL,13,Fstandards in adult social care.
OL,15,F"A fundamental mismatch"
OL,17,FThe high cost of private sector
OL,18,Fplacements, increasing demand for
OL,19,Fspecial educational needs support, and
OL,20,Fworkforce challenges were cited as key
OL,21,Fissues.
