OL,3,CCash-strapped Midlands councils call
OL,4,Cfor government help
OL,6,FIn his letter, Sir Stephen warned of a
OL,7,F"fundamental mismatch" between the
OL,8,Fresources available to local
OL,9,Fauthorities and their growing
OL,10,Fresponsibilities.
OL,12,FHe highlighted the urgent need for
OL,13,Fcouncil tax equalisation and long-term
OL,14,Ffinancial certainty, as many councils,
OL,15,Fparticularly in poorer areas, are
OL,16,Fincreasingly reliant on council tax
OL,17,Frevenue while central government
OL,18,Ffunding has been reduced.
