OL,3,CCash-strapped Midlands councils call
OL,4,Cfor government help
OL,6,FThe uncertainty surrounding the 2025-
OL,7,F26 local government financial
OL,8,Fsettlement and spending review has
OL,9,Fcaused over three-quarters of councils
OL,10,Fto defer projects, with nearly a third
OL,11,Freducing activities to cut costs.
OL,13,FSigoma is calling for a 7% increase in
OL,14,Fcore spending power for 2025-26 and an
OL,15,Fannual increase aligned with inflation
OL,16,Fto address the funding gap.
OL,18,FSome councils, such as Birmingham and
OL,19,FNottingham, have already declared
OL,20,Feffective bankruptcy.
