OL,3,CCash-strapped Midlands councils call
OL,4,Cfor government help
OL,6,FThe government has promised multi-year
OL,7,Ffunding settlements and reforms, but
OL,8,Flocal authorities in the Midlands and
OL,9,Fbeyond are calling for more immediate
OL,10,Fand comprehensive support to avoid
OL,11,Ffurther service cuts and financial
OL,12,Finstability.
